parameters:
\SE[2]Well, well... My, my, a self-declared princess going
into battle herself. \SE[1]Isn't that a bit too tomboyish?

\SE[54]Hmph, I can afford to be confident for now! It's been
a hundred years since we last met...! \SE[50]Your barbaric
actions end here!!

\SE[38]Honestly, I've never liked you guys from the
beginning! \SE[54]This is a perfect opportunity! I'll
personally take care of you right here!!

\SE[14]Hehehe... Quite spirited, aren't you? \SE[1]Very
well, I shall have some fun with you. It's time for a lesson
in the ways of the world, naive princess.
\SE[0] (They're not here... Is this war just a facade...?)
